[20/01/2019 22:40:32] <font color="#ffffff">¡Ya!</font>
[20/01/2019 22:40:34] <font color="#ffffff">Bueno, eh...</font>
[20/01/2019 22:40:34] <font color="#ffffff">Nos pidieron que le avisáramos</font>
